\\nassistant: 现在我明白了！OpenClaw 有两个 skills 目录：\\n\\n1. **系统 skills**: `/home/workplace/openclaw/skills/` (内置)\\n2. **用户 skills**: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` (您的 imap-smtp-email 在这里)\\n\\n**问题原因：**\\n\\nOpenClaw 默认只加载系统 skills。用户 skills 目录需要正确配置才能被识别。\\n\\n让我检查是否需要在配置中添加：\\nassistant: 让我查看 OpenClaw 的 skills 配置文档：\\nassistant: 找到原因了！根据文档，skills 加载路径优先级\\n\\nSource: memory/2026-04-10-i-m-ready-to-help-i-can-see-th.md#L77-L110\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/2026-04-10-i-m-ready-to-help-i-can-see-th.md#L77-L110\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"mode\": \"fts-only\"\n}"}],"details":{"results":[{"id":"102c885dd77d71da340f99a1954b57d80f444141071bb6ae9b1e4a3e58d91a75","path":"memory/2026-04-10-i-m-ready-to-help-i-can-see-th.md","startLine":102,"endLine":144,"score":0.0000018928222732122888,"textScore":0.0000018928222732122888,"snippet":"2. `<workspace>/.agents/skills`\n3. `~/.agents/skills`\n4. `~/.openclaw/skills`\n5. bundled skills\n6. `skills.load.extraDirs` (最低优先级)\n\n您的 workspace 是 `/home/chinalife/.openclaw/workspace`，所以 `<workspace>/skills` 应该是 `/home/chinalife/.openclaw/workspace/skills`。\n\n让我验证路径：\nassistant: 路径正确！让我检查会话状态看看 skills 加载情况：\nassistant: 让我检查 SKILL.md 格式：\nassistant: SKILL.md 格式正确。问题可能是：\n\n1. **会话启动时 skill 已存在但未被识别**\n2. **配置中可能有 allowlist 限制**\n\n让我检查配置：\nassistant: **找到原因了！**\n\n您的 `imap-smtp-email` skill 位置正确，格式也正确。但 **skills 在会话启动时加载**，当前会话是在您安装该 skill 之前启动的。\n\n**解决方案：**\n\n1. **重启会话** - 最简单的方法，新会话会自动加载 workspace skills\n\n2. **或者手动触发重新加载** - 如果 Gateway 配置了 `skills.load.watch: true`（默认），修改 SKILL.md 可以触发重新加载：\n   ```bash\n\nSource: memory/2026-04-10-i-m-ready-to-help-i-can-see-th.md#L102-L144","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-04-10-i-m-ready-to-help-i-can-see-th.md#L102-L144","corpus":"memory"},{"id":"3ce502abcd41969b8b6f9a61c5ebaaf0c10be40871f2f5d91d156e6058d7a3e8","path":"memory/2026-04-10-i-m-ready-to-help-i-can-see-th.md","startL