{"type":"message","id":"26a4bce0","parentId":"5a355125","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:21:53.272Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found 3 emails from the last 10 minutes. Let me analyze them for urgency:\n\n1. UID 23 - \"SMTP Connection Test\" from nwftool@sina.com - This is a test email, not urgent\n2. UID 21 - \"系统退信\" (System Bounce) from MAILER-DAEMON - This is a bounced email notification, could be considered urgent as it indicates a delivery failure\n3. UID 19 - \"SMTP Connection Test\" from nwftool@sina.com - Another test email, not urgent\n\nOnly the bounced email (UID 21) could be considered somewhat urgent as it indicates a delivery failure. However, this is from a test email that was sent to an invalid address (recipient@example.com), so it's not truly urgent.\n\nLet me check if there are any other emails with keywords that might indicate urgency. Let me search for emails with keywords like \"urgent\", \"deadline\", \"meeting\", \"immediate\", \"紧急\", \"截止\", \"会议\" etc.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Let me search for emails with urgency-related keywords."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_077cff3a10694117ae0c2f58","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node /home/chinalife/.openclaw/workspace/skills/imap-smtp-email/scripts/imap.js search --recent 10m --limit 50"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-wishub-x6-ctyun-cn","model":"GLM-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775809301208,"responseId":"a843f1398b0c419097cbb93f08cd83b2"}}
